description: Our Premier Collection is a nod to the very finest designs and features our most sumptuous ranges of furniture. Our Premier Collection contains stylish sofas, cosy armchairs and gorgeous dining chairs to suit a plethora of environments. These lovingly crafted, specially styled artisan items are oozing class and sophistication, celebrating the very best aesthetics of high end furniture. Our Premier Collection can be customised with your choice of materials too! All items which contain foam and/or fabric are CRIB 5 Certified unless otherwise stated.
